Android Changes
---------------
We addressed a significant number of [issues](http://jira.appcelerator.org/secure/IssueNavigator.jspa?mode=hide&requestId=12037), including: 

*Features:*

- The big feature for Android this release is dual-runtime support. We added support for V8 as a runtime and have made it the default.
- Debugging support in V8 [TIMOB-6190](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-6190)
- Animation of backgroundColor [TIMOB-5460](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-5460)
- Allow multiple attachments to Email Dialog [TIMOB-837](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-837)
- Support for long press event [TIMOB-1653](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-1653)
- Support gzip and deflate encodings on HTTPClient [TIMOB-2698](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-2698)
- Expose Window Pixel Format on Heavyweight Windows [TIMOB-4104](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-4104)
- Enable plugins for WebViews [TIMOB-1607](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-1607)
- Expose Keep Screen On for Views [TIMOB-2102](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-2102)
- [JIRA List of all Android Features](http://jira.appcelerator.org/secure/IssueNavigator.jspa?mode=hide&requestId=12124)

*Bug Fixes:*

- Change zIndex at runtime [TIMOB-1729](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-1729)
- Embedded video support. Parity with iOS [TIMOB-2565](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-2565) - Previous default behavior, since we couldn't add the player to a parent view, was that fullscreen would be true. That's not the case for iOS, and for parity's sake it's no longer the case for Android now that we can put the player on a view. So if fullscreen is desired now in Android, you must specifically set fullscreen to true.
- Support devices w/o sdcards [TIMOB-2613](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-2613)
- Updates to opacity and animation [TIMOB-2851](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-2851)
- Build failures with Subversion [TIMOB-3021](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-3021)
- Scroll view doesn't scroll horizontally [TIMOB-3296](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-3296)
- XML.parseString not detected [TIMOB-3465](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-3465)
- Webview crashes on reopen [TIMOB-4357](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-4357)
- Support for SDK Tools r14/r15 style add-on folders [TIMOB-6135](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-6135)
